---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="standards — the keepers." description="How we source, name names, handle conflicts, and correct errors." current="standards">
  <div class="container container-narrow page">
    <p class="ui-label">editorial standards</p>
    <h1>how we report. who we <em>name</em>. what we will not do.</h1>
    <h2>sourcing.</h2>
    <p>Every profile is reported. Subjects are interviewed in person where possible. Facts are checked against public records (Assessor, Secretary of State, court filings, BPLA). Quotations are <em>verbatim</em> unless marked otherwise.</p>
    <h2>naming.</h2>
    <p>We name a landlord, a chain, a public official, or a corporate party when their action is the public-interest hinge of the story and we can independently verify the claim. We do <em>not</em> name a subject's family member, employer, or address without their consent unless that information is already public and material.</p>
    <h2>conflicts of interest.</h2>
    <p>Sponsored entries on best of lists carry a labeled badge. Sponsors do not pick stories or entries. The editor who names a list is named on the list. We do not run affiliate links. We do not accept gifts above <em>twenty-five</em> dollars from subjects.</p>
    <h2>ai.</h2>
    <p>No byline on this site is AI-generated. No article is partially or substantially written by AI. Editing tools (spell check, grammar suggestions) are allowed. Generation tools are not.</p>
    <h2>corrections.</h2>
    <p>Errors are corrected on the article page with a dated note. All corrections are also logged at <a href="/corrections">/corrections</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page { padding-block: var(--s-9); }
  .page h1 {
    margin-block: var(--s-3) var(--s-5);
    max-width: 22ch;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 30;
  }
  .page h1 :global(em) {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 80, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page h2 {
    margin-block: var(--s-7) var(--s-3);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 80, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page p { margin-bottom: var(--s-4); }
  .page p em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 16, 'WONK' 1;
  }
  .page a { color: var(--terracotta); border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor; }
</style>
